ActNunavut Act
SubjectTransfer of parcels of land to the Commissioner of Nunavut
PrecisOrder TRANSFERING TO THE COMMISSIONER OF NUNAVUT the administration and control of several surveyed parcels of land (approximatively 5,727 square metres), comprising the beds of bodies of water within several ponds that lie within the municipal boundaries of the HAMLET OF KUGLUKTUK.
